description: One of the risks with doing live shows is that anything can happen. In this case Bryce Star's routine flight from L.A. is delayed over 5 hours, leaving Ryan Wild to open the show by himself. Luckily there's no one cuter than Ryan, whose boyish charm keeps the live audience entertained until Bryce shows up. The two cute studs compare tattoos and waste no time getting down to some serious dick-sucking. Ryan proves to be quite the cocksucker as he milks a creamy load out of Bryce who says the blowjob was worth the trip!
title: Bryce Star And Ryan Wild, Scene #01
